“doxentral” is CI based file sharing web app.

-> Add new users
-> Upload files
-> Assign files to other users
-> Users can upload new files. They can download files admin has assigned to them.

Uses SWFUpload (http://www.swfupload.org/), jQuery::ColorBox (http://colorpowered.com/colorbox/)

1) db.sql has the DDL required to setup initial database.

You may have to modify the following config files before attempting to run the app.
database.php
config.php
settings.php